wikipedia_page.main: Annette Doreen Campbell (born (1961-10-24)24 October 1961) is a British weightlifter, competing in the 63 kg category and representing England and Great Britain at international competitions. She competed at world championships, most recently at the 2003 World Weightlifting Championships.
